#

Creamy Mashed Potatoes

35 min
$5.5
400 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodSide Dish

Description

Rich and creamy mashed potatoes, perfect as a comforting side dish.

Ingredients

  • russet potatoes: 2 lbs
  • butter: 1/2 cup
  • heavy cream: 1/2 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1/2 tsp
